            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel the <strong>ginger </strong>(scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways and deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon)</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, reserving some leaves for garnish</p><p>Peel and finely slice the<strong> brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
